data.description: This incredible pool home sits in the heart of Cape Coral on an oversized corner lot! The 4 bedrooms and 2 baths home greets you with a bright open floor plan and tile throughout. Brand new pool heater installed in 2022 so you can enjoy your heated pool year round. Save on your electric bill with PAID OFF Solar Panels; Roof 2014; AC 2011.  (home suffered minimal damage with Hurricane Ian and the damages have been fixed)
